title: 13 Piece Professional Series™ Stainless Set Demo (89-13)
description: Cook like a pro with this professional stainless steel cookware from Cuisinart. The exclusive PowerBond™ high impact bonded base heats fast, distributes heat evenly, and is induction cooktop ready. Riveted stainless handles provide strength and durability for ultimate control. Tempered glass FlavorLock® lids seal in moisture and nutrients, cookware is oven and broiler-safe up to 500°F for superior versatility. Glass lids oven safe up to 350°F.
